#: ../../B/big-win.rst:13
msgid ""
"[MIT] Serendipity. \"Yes, those two physicists discovered high-temperature "
"superconductivity in a batch of ceramic that had been prepared incorrectly "
"according to their experimental schedule. Small mistake; big win!\" See "
":ref:`win-big`\\."
msgstr ""
"[MIT]思わぬ幸運(serendipity)。「そう、あの2人の物理学者は、実験計画に照らして誤って調製されたセラミックの一群の中に、高温超伝導を発見したんだ。小さなミス、大きな勝利(big"
" win)さ!」\\ :ref:`win-big`\\ を参照。"
